      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WOOLGOOLGA (1) jumps from the inside draw. Latest effort finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on June 6 over 520m at this track behind Super Sassy beaten 2.5 lengths (30.16). Looks well placed here and rates a key player. Expected to be in the finish. GREAT CHAT (5) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 5 lengths at Gosford in a handy 29.55 beating Real Bonnie. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Bold showing expected again. DARK NOISE (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.5 lengths second (24.50) behind Taw Galaxy at Goulburn. Form from her last run is proving strong. Must be included in calculations. DAISY'S CHARM (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.",
